== 製作 ==
=== 拍攝 ===
[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2015年5月18日在[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]開始進行<ref>{{cite web |author=Sokol, Tony |url=http://www.denofgeek.us/movies/leatherface/246002/nu-image-adds-leatherface-to-cannes-market |title=Nu Image Adds Leatherface To Cannes Market |publisher=Den of Geek |date=2015-05-05 |accessdate=2015-06-03 |archive-date=2015-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151227074925/http://www.denofgeek.us/movies/leatherface/246002/nu-image-adds-leatherface-to-cannes-market |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Bloody Disgusting 3">{{cite news|last1=Miska|first1=Brad|title='Leatherface' Cast, Crew and Location Shots!|url=https://bloody-disgusting.com/images/3346858/leatherface-cast-crew-location-shots/|accessdate=2015-06-03|publisher=[[Bloody_Disgusting|Bloody Disgusting]]|date=2015-05-28|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421163349/https://bloody-disgusting.com/images/3346858/leatherface-cast-crew-location-shots/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Bloody Disgusting 5-29-15">{{cite news|last1=Miska|first1=Brad|title=One More On the Run From 'Leatherface' (Exclusive)|url=https://bloody-disgusting.com/exclusives/3346977/one-run-leatherface-exclusive/|accessdate=2015-06-04|publisher=[[Bloody_Disgusting|Bloody Disgusting]]|date=2015-05-29|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421163354/https://bloody-disgusting.com/exclusives/3346977/one-run-leatherface-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，拍攝地點和場景與[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]的地形相似，並向該系列的先前電影致敬。

== 發行 ==
《德州電鋸殺人狂前傳：皮面人》由[[獅門影視公司|獅門影視公司]]定於2017年10月20日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last=Kennedy|first=Michael|title=Texas Chainsaw Massacre Prequel Leatherface Sets Release Date|url=https://screenrant.com/texas-chainsaw-prequel-leatherface-release-date/|website=Screen Rant|date=2017-06-20|accessdate=2017-06-30|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421163349/https://screenrant.com/texas-chainsaw-prequel-leatherface-release-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|last=Sandwell|first=Ian|title=FrightFest 2017 to open with 'Cult Of Chucky' starring Jennifer Tilly|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/frightfest-2017-to-open-with-cult-of-chucky-starring-jennifer-tilly/5119551.article|magazine=Screen Daily|date=2017-06-30|accessdate=2017-06-30|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421163354/https://www.screendaily.com/news/frightfest-2017-to-open-with-cult-of-chucky-starring-jennifer-tilly/5119551.article|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Foutch|first=Haleigh|title='Leatherface': 'Texas Chainsaw' Prequel Finally Gets a Release Date and Brutal First-Look Images|url=http://collider.com/leatherface-released-date-texas-chainsaw-massacre-prequel/|website=Collider|date=2017-06-30|accessdate=2017-07-01|archive-date=2018-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181018103748/http://collider.com/leatherface-released-date-texas-chainsaw-massacre-prequel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據44條評論，持有30%的新鮮度，平均得分4.10／10，觀眾投票獲得24%的分數，平均得分為2.43／5<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/leatherface_2017|title=Leatherface (2017)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421163351/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/leatherface_2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得40分<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/leatherface|title=Leatherface Reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2021-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211022180208/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/leatherface|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

